headline: Lamb Weston to Close Munro, Argentina Plant, Consolidating Latin America Production to State-of-the-Art Mar del Plata Facility
summary: EAGLE, Idaho, January 08, 2026--Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) announced today plans to close its Munro, Argentina plant and consolidate production for the Latin America region to its new, modern facility in Mar del Plata, Argentina.
